<font color=#ffffff>(6/19/01 3:24:10 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Try being proactive...</span><hr size=1> Instead of waiting for someone to &quot;draft&quot; you for a group, try putting one together yourself.  <br>
<br>
You have a great core--tank and cleric.  Grab an enchanter for some crowd control.  Grab a druid or wizzie for snare/evac duties.  Then you can just fill in the holes from there...  <br>
<br>
Groups don't just come out of thin air--somebody has to put it together.  I can't see why that group leader can't be you...<br>
<br>
Also, I find if you take off the /roleplay or /anon put on a /LFG tag and sit in a popular zone (like LowerGuk, Dreadlands or SolB for your level or Karnors/TT/Sebilis when you get a little higher), your chances of being &quot;drafted&quot; go up tremendously.  <br>
<br>
/shouting, /ooc'ing or /guildspaming a group request is not very efficient or effective.  It only seems to work when one spot is needed or someone is leaving, otherwise it goes ignored by the others who are looking for a group as well or already in a group.  <br>
<br>
If more people were more pro-active...  there'd be a lot less people sitting at the zones playing /gems waiting for that magical /tell &quot;we got a group for you!&quot;.  <br>
<br>
Jus' some thoughts...<br>
<br>
--Bakxs<br>
www.eqendless.com<br>
<br>
P.S.  Jus' because you are proactive doesn't meant you will find a group right away--but it helps.  =) <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm5.showMessage?topicID=182.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm5.showMessage?topicID=171.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm5.threadControl?topicID=183.topic><img src=http://sirion.netfirms.com/vcc/deleteThread.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm5.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=183.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm5.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=183.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub41.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="vazaellecommunitycenterfrm2">Vazaelle Server Board Rules<option value="vazaellecommunitycenterfrm6">Guild Links<option value="vazaellecommunitycenterfrm1">General Discussion<option value="vazaellecommunitycenterfrm4">The Bazaar<option value="vazaellecommunitycenterfrm12">The Voting Booth<option value="vazaellecommunitycenterfrm3">Events Scheduling<option value="vazaellecommunitycenterfrm8">The Gallery<option value="vazaellecommunitycenterfrm5">Rants and Flames<option value="vazaellecommunitycenterfrm7">Vazaelle Guild Leader Lounge<option value="vazaellecommunit